text.tspan: Goals & Needs
Everyday Activities
Motivations
Erin needs to find pieces that can easily be covered
when she is working or at school.
Due to her strict schedule, she needs to have the
ability to book her appointments months in
advance.
She is a make-up artist, so she likes to be creative.
She needs to have some creative direction in the
ink that she gets.
Erin is up at 6:00 am every morning to get her
daughter to school by 7:30.
Meets with clients and holds consultations for
make-up tutorials
Is always on Instagram featuring her client
portfolio and building her book of business. She
loves to surf IG and Pinterest for tattoo inspired
ideas.
Attends school 3 days out of the week.
Erin is motivated by her family. She puts family
before anything.
She is an artist, and she is motivated by creating
and making things beautiful.
She is really into make-up/body art and anything
feminine. Erin loves making people feel good and
she wants her ink to evoke feelings of happiness
and joy.
Frustrations
Erin’s Direct Quotes
Erin has very sensitive skin, so it is hard for her
to find tattoo related knowledge-bases to do her
research tattoo up-keep.
She hates feeling like she cannot have any
creative input when she is getting a new tattoo.
Being away from her family for long periods of
time, and poor customer service really
frustrates her.
“I would love an app that is a one-stop shop for
everything tattoo related.”
“My family is my everything! My favorite tattoo is
my daughter Kailah’s name on my wrist.”
“I work in the beauty industry and love to make
people feel beautiful. I want to wear beautiful
works of art to inspire those around me.”
Device & Internet Usage
Erin Ortiz
“ The Make-up Mommy”
Erin is a 28-year-old mother and a make-
up artist in Riverside, CA. Currently, she is
pursing her degree in cosmetology.
As a full-time mother and make-up artist,
Erin is always busy. On top of her work
and home life, she is also completing her
degree in cosmetology. Between her
work, school and home life, she bounces
between her computer and mobile
device.
Erin enjoys the company of other
people, but she cherishes the time she
spends with her family.
